Jarvis Addams is Frankie's older brother who gets married to Janice Evans. A completely absent figure from the immediate action, he becomes the source of all Frankie's desires and fantasies. She spent two years dreaming about him while he was stationed in Alaska, and now all she can think about is somehow joining in on his marriage. However hard Frankie tries to convince herself that she is an adult, Jarvis still sees her as a little kid.